rComments: This was a pretty interesting course. I liked it. It was annoying being graded on participation and attendance (15%), but she's hot. Made the class fun to attend ;)

One of the best professors I have had in my undergrad! She's very down to earth, and very knowledgeable about the topic/course. The course is very organized and she provides lots of examples! Would definitely recommend!

Still haven't been evaluated (might change my mind after her evaluation LOL), but she's a very personable prof. Her style of teaching is cool and genuine. Attendance is mandatory but the material is not too difficult to digest
